data.description: Back on the Market!! Now Showing! Welcome to the Sendera Ranch Community. Located in the Northwest Independent School district, this 5 bedroom 4 bath 2 story 3,409 sqft  home  has the space your looking for. Catch a view at the granite countertops in the kitchen. Then move to the cozy living area then on to the Primary bedroom with lots of bathroom space. The home also has one main room downstairs. Let's go upstairs, where you will walk right into a large game area or second living area. There are 3 more spacious bedrooms upstairs along with a theater room to boast. Home comes Equipped with solar panels. What is a home without neighbors! Come on down to the community pool and have a blast with some friends.
